01/09/2005
PRISTINA, Kosovo, Serbia-Montenegro -- Italian Lieutenant General Giuseppe Valotto formally assumes command of KFOR troops from French Lieutenant General Yves de Kermabon during a ceremony Thursday (1 September). Several officials are attending the ceremony, but not Kosovo President Ibrahim Rugova, who is reportedly suffering complications from a bout with the flu. He remains hospitalised at a US military facility in Germany after being flown there Saturday for tests. (Tanjug, AFP, AP, Reuters - 31/08/05)
